comments.body:
is 

```c++
_hist = new TH1D(histName(),"A RooPlot",100,xmin,xmax);
_hist->SetDirectory(nullptr);
```

strictly equivalent to

```c++
TH1::AddDirectory(kFALSE);
_hist = new TH1D(histName(),"A RooPlot",100,xmin,xmax);
```
?

There might be some global state change in the first version that is skipped in the second, not sure if it can have user-visible consequences... @pcanal ?

